<h2>Chapter 2: What Requires AI Disclosure and What Does Not &#123;#ch2&#125;</h2>
<p>Not every use of AI in marketing requires disclosure. The FTC distinguishes between cosmetic uses of AI and substantive uses that affect how consumers interpret the content.</p>
<h3>Content That Requires AI Disclosure</h3>
